{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"4294967294","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"pt-BR\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/30ab0c22ec89909a.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-a276241ddc960958.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-119f940f59a4d5f9.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/684-9cfdbd6f2bfacd4f.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-c8cd4f7f21d08dc5.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/607-1451ee05c69949dc.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/page-cd9a7c87c071cb4c.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>ABCResolve — Encontre profissionais no Grande ABC</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Conectamos você aos melhores prestadores de serviços do Grande ABC: Santo André, São Bernardo, São Caetano, Diadema, Mauá e mais.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"serviços, profissionais, ABC, Santo André, São Bernardo, eletricista, encanador, pintor, faxineira\"/><script>document.querySelectorAll('body link[rel=\"icon\"], body link[rel=\"apple-touch-icon\"]').forEach(el => document.head.appendChild(el))</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-100 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-extrabold text-xl text-primary-700\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div>ABC<span class=\"text-accent-500\">Resolve</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#como-funciona\">Como funciona</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#categorias\">Serviços</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Pedir orçamento</a></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"btn-accent text-sm py-2\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço</a><a class=\"btn-secondary text-sm py-2\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Sou prestador</a></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-700 via-primary-600 to-primary-500 text-white py-20 md:py-28 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-white via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 border border-white/30\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg>Profissionais verificados no Grande ABC</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight\">Encontre o profissional certo para <span class=\"text-yellow-300\">qualquer serviço</span></h1><p class=\"mt-5 text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-100 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">Do eletricista ao professor particular — conectamos você a prestadores de serviço de confiança em Santo André, São Bernardo, São Caetano, Diadema e toda a região do ABC.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3\"><a class=\"btn-accent text-base py-4 px-8 shadow-lg\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço gratuito</a><a class=\"bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border border-white/40 transition-all duration-200 text-base text-center\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Sou prestador de serviço</a></div><p class=\"mt-4 text-primary-200 text-sm flex items-center gap-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg> Grátis para clientes · Rápido · Sem compromisso</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-primary-900 text-white py-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center\"><div><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-yellow-400\">...</div><div class=\"text-sm text-primary-300 mt-1\">Prestadores cadastrados</div></div><div><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-yellow-400\">...</div><div class=\"text-sm text-primary-300 mt-1\">Serviços realizados</div></div><div><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-yellow-400\">...</div><div class=\"text-sm text-primary-300 mt-1\">Cidades atendidas</div></div><div><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-yellow-400\">...</div><div class=\"text-sm text-primary-300 mt-1\">Avaliação média</div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"categorias\" class=\"py-20 bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">O que você precisa hoje?</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">Escolha a categoria e encontre o profissional ideal</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4\"><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 border-orange-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=aulas\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">📚</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Aulas e Cursos</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-600 border-yellow-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=beleza\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">💇</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Beleza e Estética</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 border-blue-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=encanamento\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🔧</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Encanamento</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 border-purple-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=eventos\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🎉</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Eventos e Festas</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-green-50 text-green-600 border-green-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=jardinagem\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🌱</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Jardinagem</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 border-emerald-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=limpeza\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🧹</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Limpeza e Organização</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 border-gray-200 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=eletrica\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">⚡</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Manutenção Elétrica</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 border-indigo-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=mudancas\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🚛</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Mudanças e Fretes</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-pink-50 text-pink-600 border-pink-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=pintura\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🎨</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Pintura</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 border-rose-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=reformas\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🔨</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Reformas e Construção</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-red-50 text-red-600 border-red-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=saude\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">🏥</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Saúde e Bem-estar</span></a><a class=\"card flex flex-col items-center gap-3 p-5 text-center border-2 bg-violet-50 text-violet-600 border-violet-100 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 cursor-pointer\" href=\"/solicitar-servico?categoria=tecnologia\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/60 text-2xl\">💻</div><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold leading-tight\">Tecnologia e TI</span></a></div><div class=\"text-center mt-8\"><a class=\"btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Ver todos os serviços <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"como-funciona\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-14\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Como funciona</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">Em 3 passos simples você resolve tudo</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-1/4 right-1/4 h-0.5 bg-primary-100\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search text-primary-600\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><path d=\"m21 21-4.3-4.3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow\">1</div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Descreva o serviço</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Conte o que você precisa, onde e quando. Leva menos de 2 minutos.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star text-primary-600\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow\">2</div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Receba orçamentos</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Profissionais da sua região entram em contato com orçamentos personalizados.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4\"><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-primary-600\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow\">3</div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Escolha e contrate</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Compare avaliações, escolha o melhor profissional e feche o negócio.</p></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-12\"><a class=\"btn-primary text-base py-4 px-10\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Começar agora — é grátis!</a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-primary-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\"><div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Por que escolher o ABCResolve?</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Somos a plataforma focada na região do Grande ABC. Conhecemos sua vizinhança.</p><ul class=\"mt-8 space-y-5\"><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Profissionais verificados</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0.5\">Todos os prestadores passam por análise antes de aparecer na plataforma.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Resposta rápida</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0.5\">Receba orçamentos em até 24 horas após sua solicitação.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Avaliações reais</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0.5\">Leia as opiniões de quem já contratou antes de decidir.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">100% gratuito para clientes</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0.5\">Você não paga nada para solicitar serviços e receber orçamentos.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-primary-100\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-6\">É prestador de serviço?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Cadastre-se gratuitamente e receba pedidos de clientes na sua região. Você decide quais serviços aceitar.</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Receba pedidos de clientes próximos</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Mostre seus trabalhos e avaliações</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Sem mensalidade — só quando fechar negócio</li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Atenda na sua cidade ou região</li></ul><a class=\"btn-primary block text-center\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Quero me cadastrar como prestador</a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"testimonials-section\" class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">O que dizem nossos clientes</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">Carregando depoimentos...</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-primary-500 text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4\">Pronto para resolver?</h2><p class=\"text-primary-100 text-lg mb-8\">Descreva o que você precisa e receba orçamentos de profissionais da sua região em minutos.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn-accent text-base py-4 px-10 shadow-lg\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço agora</a><a class=\"bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl border border-white/40 transition-all duration-200\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Cadastrar como prestador</a></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-extrabold text-xl text-white mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div>ABC<span class=\"text-accent-500\">Resolve</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Conectamos você aos melhores profissionais da região do Grande ABC.</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-primary-400\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>Grande ABC — SP</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone text-primary-400\"><path d=\"M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1